[SN]TITLE[SN]
Driver injured in 'road rage' attack in Dumbarton

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has been injured after being attacked by another driver following a "road rage" incident near Dumbarton.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The drivers of a silver Ford Focus and a white Peugeot van were involved in a dispute on the A82, at its Glasgow Road junction, at about 16:20 on Monday.
Both vehicles later stopped on Glasgow Road, near Dumbarton town centre. An altercation took place and the Ford Focus driver sustained a head injury.
Police have appealed for witnesses to the incident to get in touch.
